input.sql:
select 
 ARRAY_TO_STRING(OPPORTUNITY_ROLES, ', ') AS OPPORTUNITY_ROLES
,TRX_NUMBER
,TRX_DATE
, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS JOURNAL_DATE
,TRX_DATE_FISCAL_QUARTER_SHORTNAME
,TRX_DATE_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER
,TRX_DATE_FISCAL_YEAR_NAME
,TRX_CRM_FORECAST_CATEGORY
,TRX_COUNTRY_OF_ORDER
,TRX_SPLIT_COVERAGE_SEGMENT
,SOURCE_ROUTE_TO_MARKET
,TRX_ROUTE_TO_MARKET
,TRX_STATUS,TRX_TYPE
,TRX_SOURCE
,TRX_CLOSED_BOOKING_FLAG
,TRANSACTION_TYPE
,PRODUCT_CODE
,PARTNER_ALIGNMENT_FOR_REBATES
,ORDERED_QUANTITY_MIN
,PRODUCT_SPLIT_OFFERING_GROUP
,TRX_PARTNER_MDM_PARTY_ID
,SNAPSHOT_DATE
,ACV_AMOUNT_USD_CY_PR_WITH_HCS_DRAWDOWN
,ACCOUNT_TYPE
,SOURCE_ID
,'Rebates' AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
,'Pending' AS STATUS
,USAGE_TYPE
,ACCOUNT_ID
,MEMBER_ID
,TRANSACTION_JOURNAL_ID
,'#{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_variable","line":"3e8f2206","path":["uat_loyalty_record_id"]}')}' AS RECORD_TYPE_ID
,'#{_dp('{"pill_type":"job_context","path":["user_name"]}')}' AS USERNAME
 from PARTNERPROGRAMS_DB.MARTS.REBATES_STAGE_TJ
 where transaction_journal_id is null
 and TRX_DATE_FISCAL_QUARTER_SHORTNAME = 'Q' ||
  CASE
    WHEN QUARTER(CURRENT_DATE) = 1 THEN 4
    ELSE QUARTER(CURRENT_DATE) - 1
  END
  || ' ' ||
  RIGHT(
    CASE
      WHEN QUARTER(CURRENT_DATE) = 1 THEN YEAR(CURRENT_DATE) - 1
      ELSE YEAR(CURRENT_DATE)
    END, 2
  )
